items.Video_Title: Quiet Luxury: A Tendência de Moda para 2023
items.Video_Description:
A mais recente tendência da indústria da moda, que está tomando conta das passarelas e das ruas, é a Quiet Luxury, uma abordagem minimalista, mas sofisticada, para o estilo de vida luxuoso. Em vez de se concentrar em peças de vestuário chamativas e ostensivas, o Quiet Luxury abraça uma abordagem mais discreta, com roupas e acessórios elegantes e minimalistas que são projetados para durar e resistir ao teste do tempo.

Nessa tendência, as roupas e acessórios luxuosos se mantém, porém muito discretos, sem mostrar que são de marcas de luxo. Um pouco diferente do que muita gente está dizendo por aí, hoje você vai entender de uma vez por todas o que é o Quiet Luxury e porque está bombando na moda 2023.

#moda2023 #tendencias2023 #luxo

Em vez de se concentrar em peças de vestuário chamativas e ostensivas, o Quiet Luxury abraça uma abordagem mais discreta, com roupas e acessórios elegantes e minimalistas que são projetados para durar e resistir ao teste do tempo.

Nessa tendência, as roupas e acessórios luxuosos se mantém, porém muito discretos, sem mostrar que são de marcas de luxo. Um pouco diferente do que muita gente está dizendo por aí, hoje você vai entender de uma vez por todas o que é o Quiet Luxury e porque está bombando na moda 2023.

items.Video_Title: Succession: Old Money vs. New Money Explained On TV
items.Video_Description:
HBO’s Succession presents a fascinating contrast between two families — The Roys and The Pierces — who represent two distinct worlds of wealth and privilege.

The Roys, who have built their vast business empire through their own hard work, determination, technology, and media, are the embodiment of the American dream of self-made success… often referred to as “new money."

The Pierces, on the other hand, represent the traditional aristocracy of America, or “old money” with their wealth and power inherited over generations and a distinct sense of “noblesse oblige” to deploy their riches for the good of the downtrodden.

--------------------------------

Top 5 OLD MONEY Communities in the NORTHEAST: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6BTmlbZqVEo&ab_channel=OldMoneyLuxury

--------------------------------

TIMESTAMPS: 

0:00 Introduction
1:21 1. The Roys Are Not “Old Money”
8:11 2. Logan’s “New Money” Faith In The Self-Made Man
11:12 3. The Pierces Are “Old Money”
14:30 4. Pierces vs. Roys: Old Money vs. New Money

--------------------------------

The Roys of New York City are a prime example of new money, with their ostentatious displays of wealth, constant bragging, and (especially as it relates to the kids), their inability to talk about anything else.

These behaviors stand in stark contrast to those of old money families, who have a generations-long tradition of discretion regarding sex, money, and politics. A simple way of understanding it could be:

“New money screams, old money whispers”

Logan Roy, the patriarch of the family, is a self-made man who has amassed a massive fortune, but he is not without his insecurities.

He is acutely aware of his status as "new money" and carries a significant chip on his shoulder as a result.

His marriage to Catherine, a member of the British aristocracy, is a clear indication of his desire to elevate his family’s standing in society.

Despite this fact, Logan is deeply critical of the old castes of Europe, the exploitation of the poor by the wealthy class, and even the fat titans of media that he destroyed when he was young.

His contempt for the old guard is palpable, and his desire to forge a new path for himself and his family is evident in everything he does.

The younger generation of clan Roy takes up this model and goes to the extremes of new money culture in their behaviors.

Since Logan raised them and their English aristocratic mother didn't pay much attention to them, they represent a new kind of wealth that is marked by excess and a lack of sophistication.

Kendall Roy, the on-and-off heir apparent to the Roy Empire, is first shown (and then many times after throughout the show) in a manner that speaks to his unrefined nature.

His obsession with rap music and unrefined rhyming is a clear departure from the more sophisticated musical preferences of the old money elite.

This serves as a reminder of the fundamental differences between old money and new money, and how they are reflected in even the most seemingly insignificant details of one’s behavior and lifestyle.

Furthermore, Kendall’s social skills are often lacking, as he struggles to connect with others on a personal level and often comes across as awkward or uncomfortable in social situations.

This lack of refinement is another hallmark of new money, as those who have inherited their wealth and status often receive extensive training in etiquette and social graces from an early age.

Lastly, both Kendall is prone to making impulsive and rash decisions, such as his ill-fated attempt to take over the company from his father in the first season.

This lack of patience and foresight is often associated with those who have suddenly acquired their wealth and power, rather than those who have inherited it over generations. This is a trait that is consistently exemplified by Shiv, Connor, and Roman as well.

Indeed, Logan’s other son, Roman, is an example of the shallow and indulgent lifestyle that is often associated with new money.

His hedonistic and impulsive lifestyle is characterized by a lack of concern for basic societal norms and a preference for base pleasures.

For instance, Roman’s casual and flippant approach to sex is indicative of his unrefined nature. His preference for older women and lack of discretion is a stark contrast to the old money elite, who place a high value on propriety and decorum.

Furthermore, Roman’s ignorance of basic household items, like a gallon of milk, is yet another indication of his unrefined and privileged background.

Those who have inherited their wealth and status over generations are often more attuned to the value of money and the practicalities of everyday life, while new money individuals like Roman are insulated from such concerns.

items.Video_Title: QUIET LUXURY: O Conceito de usar grife sem ostentar I Viih Rocha
items.Video_Description:
Oie! No vídeo de hoje, vou compartilhar com vocês dicas valiosas sobre como adotar o conceito de "Quiet Luxury" no seu guarda-roupa. Esse conceito tem ficado cada vez mais forte na internet e eu tenho visto muito mitos sendo criados. E para que você possa entender e aplicar corretamente no seu estilo, vamos nos aprofundar nesse assunto. 

O "Quiet Luxury" é uma abordagem elegante e discreta para usar marcas de luxo sem ostentar. Vou mostrar como incorporar peças-chave e acessórios sofisticados em seu estilo, sem chamar muita atenção, mas se mantendo fiel ao seu senso de moda. 

Neste vídeo, você aprenderá como selecionar roupas de qualidade, escolher itens atemporais que transcenderão as tendências passageiras e criar looks refinados e sofisticados. Além disso, vou compartilhar dicas sobre como equilibrar peças de grife com itens mais acessíveis, para criar um guarda-roupa versátil e elegante.

Quero que você aprenda e abra sua mente para construir seu estilo e se sentir confiante, sem comprometer seu orçamento. Se você é apaixonada por moda feminina e deseja explorar o mundo do luxo de forma discreta, este vídeo é perfeito para você. 

E aí, curtiu esse conceito? 

Com amor, Viih. 

✨

Quer se aprofundar mais em moda? Minha mentoria te ajuda. Transforme-se de dentro pra fora, da cabeça aos pés com o SE ENXERGA. Entre na lista de espera: https://viihrocha.com/lista-espera-se-enxerga/

Hello, my luxurious friends, 
I watch a lot of luxury content and I've seen the old money aesthetic and quiet luxury trends explode recently. Quiet luxury brands are brands like Polene, Delvaux (which is both quiet and really expensive), Longchamp, etc. Or any bag/shoe/accessory from a brand that doesn't display a massive logo. 
I think it's fine to like a certain trendy style or buy items that don't have logos for a different type of look, but this seems to be turning into something more. 
I have some thoughts about why people are so intense when it comes to "quiet luxury" and "old money aesthetic". 

Hope you enjoy. Let me know your thoughts in the comments! 

IG: itskateswan
email: lovekatenicole@gmail.com

items.Video_Title: Quiet Luxury Aesthetic: how do rich people actually dress?  | Street Style
items.Video_Description:
Subscribe to our new YouTube Channel:
MILAN ON TREND Live - https://www.youtube.com/@MilanOnTrendLive

Quiet luxury is a style or approach to luxury that is understated and minimalistic instead of flashy or showy. It emphasizes the quality, craftsmanship, and materials of a product or experience, rather than overt displays of wealth or status symbols. Quiet luxury is often associated with a more refined and sophisticated aesthetic, and may appeal to those who value elegance, simplicity, and timeless design.

items.Video_Title: the DOWNFALL of expensive DESIGNER BRANDS and the RISE of QUIET LUXURY
items.Video_Description:
Hello, my luxurious friends, 
I want to talk about why some luxury content creators seem to think designer bags/clothes/shoes are done. I have some thoughts about why people are opting for "quiet luxury" brands. To me, quiet luxury brands are brands like Polene, Delvaux (which is both quiet and really expensive), Longchamp, etc. Or any bag/shoe/accessory from a brand that doesn't display a massive logo. This also seems to have a lot of crossover with the "old money aesthetic" that we've been seeing everywhere lately. 
Hope you enjoy. Let me know your thoughts in the comments!

items.Video_Title: The Rise of Quiet Luxury: Why Affluent People are Opting for Understated Fashion
items.Video_Description:
This YouTube video delves into the rising trend of quiet luxury fashion. In recent years, fashion enthusiasts have started valuing quality and elegance over flashy logos and trendy items, giving rise to this understated fashion movement. The video highlights that defining luxury can be challenging since it evolves with society, but distinguishing features that make luxury products unique can set them apart from non-luxury items. The video discusses how top luxury brands strive to maintain exclusivity, and affluent individuals opt for quiet luxury fashion to convey understated elegance and refinement while maintaining privacy and exclusivity. The video also explores how quiet luxury fashion can help individuals avoid drawing unwanted attention and becoming a target for theft or crime. The video concludes by emphasizing the importance of investing in quality basic pieces in the wardrobe to create a timeless and long-lasting fashion style. The video is informative and offers a fresh perspective on the quiet luxury trend, making it a must-watch for anyone interested in the fashion industry.

items.Video_Title: Quiet Luxury: Problematic or Trendy?
items.Video_Description:
This video is about QUIET LUXURY. The topic of quiet luxury has been trending all over the internet. Total think pieces and articles have been written about the quiet luxury fashion on the show “Succession”. Many videos on Tik Tok are giving insight on how to accomplish the quiet luxury look. But what exactly is quiet luxury?  In this video I give insight into the exact origins of quiet luxury, the exact definition, and how the idea of “old money” may be problematic. I also talk about how to find your personal style and how personal style is developed.

items.Video_Title: PURE QUIET LUXURY. Come Shopping With Me in LONDON | BAGS, LIFESTYLE VLOG & LUXURY SHOPPING.
items.Video_Description:
PURE QUIET LUXURY. Come Shopping With Me in LONDON | BAGS, LIFESTYLE VLOG & LUXURY SHOPPING.

Join me today to look at LOUIS VUITTON's newest OVERSIZED BAGS 🔥 What were they thinking for Louis Vuitton Spring Summer 2023 ?! CRAZY LUXURY SHOPPING SPREE 🔥 - 50% OFF Bicester Village GUCCI DIOR FENDI YSL 🔥 Luxury Shopping Vlog 2023 VERSACE PRADA VALENTINO BOTTEGA VENETA 😍 LONDON LUXURY SHOPPING VLOG 2023 - Let's have a look at the new Bvlgari Serpentine Pouch & the Bvlgari Serpentine Top Handle Bag as well as their classic Bvlgari Serpenti Forever Bags!! NEW IN Louis Vuitton, DIOR, CHANEL, HERMES, BVLGARI, FENDI etc. 😍 Bicester Village Haul & LUXURY BAG UNBOXING - Bicester Village LUXURY OUTLET SHOPPING VLOG 2023 😍 Let's have a look at my new Salvatore Ferragamo Gancini top handle bag - it's such a classic Salvatore Ferragamo bag!! Come Shopping With Me at Selfridges, Harrods, Hermes, Louis Vuitton, Dior, Gucci, Fendi, Bvlgari & Chanel in February 2023 !! Do you love luxury shopping vlogs as much as I do? I really missed the Bicester Village Outlet Shopping experience and I can't believe how many beautiful designer handbags I spotted!! The new Chanel Metiers d'Art 2022 Collection is finally out - otherwise known as the Chanel 22A Collection - and I've fallen in love with the pink velvet Chanel Mini Rectangular, the purple Chanel 22 Bag, the white Chanel 22S Heart Bag, the rainbow Chanel Mini Reissue and the black Chanel CC Tote which is a vintage Chanel bag that has been reissued for this year's Chanel 22B Collection!! However, the small Chanel Gabrielle Bag and the Chanel Classic Flap Bag in the Jumbo size are still next on my handbag wishlist!! I can't wait to show you more of Chanel Cruise 2023 - or Chanel 23C - which is finally coming to the boutiques soon!!

Luxury shopping in London is great, especially shopping at Gucci, Dior, Chanel & Louis Vuitton!! You never know what you'll find on a luxury shopping spree!! I love the new Bottega Veneta Teen Pouch in chlorophyll and my dream Fendi Peekaboo Mini with the embroidered flowers!! Another highlight was the Louis Vuitton Papillon Trunk Bag - they still don't have any Louis Vuitton Nano Speedy models in stock. Stay tuned for my luxury shopping haul next week - can you guess what items I bought? Maybe something from Dior - a Dior Saddle Bag, a Dior Book Tote or another Lady Dior - what do we think about Dior's new micro bags by the way? I'm in love with the micro Lady Dior!! Or maybe some Dior jewellery? I've been collecting many Dior jewelry pieces for some time now, especially Dior earrings!! I'm also a sucker for Chanel earrings and Chanel jewellery in general!! Today, we are going to visit Designer Exchange London in Knightsbridge - a reseller of vintage and pre-loved designer handbags. Stop putting down others to make yourself feel better. 

Bonjour mes amies! S’il vous plaît stop it.  Truly stop it.  This notion that certain luxuries are for certain people is more based on race than “class.” When you dress for yourself, you could care less what anyone thinks about your tax bracket. 

I don’t dress or purchase to please anyone but myself. 

If I decided to wear a monogrammed purse, so what.  If my dress is designer and doesn’t have logos, so what.  One isn’t “better” than the other. 

Remember, 99.9% of the people saying “rich people don’t do this or that” aren’t rich; they work/“observe” the “rich.” 

Ciao for now 💋

items.Video_Title: QUIET vs LOUD LUXURY & BEING JUDGED, it's a NO FROM ME.
items.Video_Description:
Gwyneth Paltrow's court case caused a stir not only for the actual case, but her understated, elegant luxury has us all talking again about slow luxury, about less in your face, logo'd, obvious luxury, less of brands who wear their logo and their recognisability proudly, and more of the understated, 'if you know, you know' type luxury. In today's video I share with you my thoughts on slow luxury, on logo's, on loud luxury, and on the judgment and assumptions that can come from wearing and loving a monogram of a logo, and takes us back to the 'poor people buy Louis Vuitton to look rich' conversation. This also ties into the new money versus old money conversation. Let me know your thoughts in the comment box.

items.Video_Title: 🔴LOOKS QUIET LUXURY para mulheres de 50, 60, 70+ anos - TENDÊNCIA 2023 PARA SENHORAS
items.Video_Description:
Bem-vindos ao nosso canal de moda! Hoje, trazemos uma tendência fascinante e elegante para todas as mulheres maduras que desejam expressar sua personalidade através do estilo: "Looks Quiet Luxury para Mulheres de 50, 60, 70 anos - Tendência 2023 para Senhoras".

Na moda contemporânea, as opções para mulheres maduras estão cada vez mais diversificadas, permitindo que elas se sintam confiantes e empoderadas em qualquer idade. Neste vídeo, vamos explorar algumas peças-chave que irão destacar sua beleza interior e realçar seu charme natural.

Começando pelos clássicos reinventados, temos o icônico jeans, uma peça versátil que pode ser facilmente adaptada para um visual sofisticado e elegante. Neste contexto, sugerimos combinar uma calça jeans de corte reto com uma blusa de seda fluída e uma jaqueta estruturada. Essa combinação harmoniosa entre casualidade e sofisticação é perfeita para um almoço com amigas ou até mesmo uma tarde de compras.

Outra tendência que está ganhando destaque são os scarpins abertos na parte de trás. Esses sapatos elegantes e femininos adicionam um toque de classe e estilo a qualquer look. Ao combiná-los com uma saia de cetim midi, você cria uma silhueta alongada e extremamente elegante. Essa é uma ótima opção para eventos mais formais ou até mesmo para uma noite especial.

As saias de cetim midi são verdadeiros coringas para mulheres maduras que buscam um visual moderno e sofisticado. Sua fluidez e caimento impecável conferem um ar de feminilidade e elegância. Aposte em cores neutras, como tons pastel, e combine-as com blusas mais ajustadas para equilibrar o look. O resultado será uma combinação perfeita entre estilo e conforto.

No quesito acessórios, as bolsas minimalistas são ideais para completar seu look "Quiet Luxury". Opte por modelos estruturados, com acabamentos de qualidade e linhas limpas. Essas bolsas conferem um toque de refinamento e sofisticação a qualquer visual, além de serem extremamente versáteis e funcionais.

Para um visual mais profissional e elegante, recomendamos investir em uma calça de alfaiataria. Esse item atemporal proporciona um caimento impecável e é perfeito para ocasiões mais formais. Combinada com uma blusa de seda ou uma camisa clássica, essa combinação é garantia de sucesso em reuniões de trabalho ou eventos sociais.

E não podemos deixar de mencionar o trench coat, um verdadeiro ícone de elegância e sofisticação. Essa peça clássica é perfeita para adicionar um toque de estilo e sofisticação aos seus looks de outono/inverno. Opte por cores neutras, como bege ou preto, e aposte em um corte estruturado que valorize sua silhueta.

Por fim, uma dica extra para elevar seu estilo é apostar em looks monocromáticos. Essa tendência simples, porém impactante, é uma ótima opção para mulheres maduras. Ao escolher uma cor e coordenar diferentes peças no mesmo tom, você cria uma aparência elegante e sofisticada. Experimente combinar tons de azul marinho ou cinza, por exemplo, para um visual refinado e moderno.

Em resumo, "Looks Quiet Luxury para Mulheres de 50, 60, 70 anos - Tendência 2023 para Senhoras" é um convite para explorar a moda de forma autêntica e versátil, com peças que exalam elegância e refinamento. Lembre-se de que a idade é apenas um número, e o estilo atemporal e sofisticado não tem limites. Aproveite as dicas e faça suas escolhas com confiança, mostrando ao mundo o quão bela e empoderada você é. Obrigado por assistir e nos vemos em breve com mais tendências e dicas de moda!

#quietluxury   #tendencias    #tendencia

items.Video_Channel_Title: Yasmina | slow fashion and personal style
items.Video_Description:
Join me for a conversation about the growing trend of quiet luxury and the timeless appeal of 'old money' fashion. In the past year, there has been a lot of buzz around the idea of understated elegance and the contrast between quiet luxury and loud luxury. Many brands have embraced the 'recession-core' style and shifted their focus to creating pieces that are both durable and classic.

In this video, I'll explore the quiet luxury aesthetic, as well as its influence on contemporary fashion. From the simplicity of minimalism to the elegance of heritage fabrics, we'll examine the key elements that define this style.

O que é quiet luxury? como ter cara de rica sem gastar muito (tendência de milhões)

Ligada a status social, uma roupa ou acessório estampado com logo de grife é facilmente reconhecível como um item caro. 

No entanto, peças mais discretas, sem cores marcantes, detalhes característicos ou símbolos aparentes, têm ganhado cada vez mais espaço na moda. 

Conhecida como "quiet luxury" (luxo quieto, em tradução livre), a tendência demonstra que ostentar não está mais tão em alta - ao menos por enquanto.

Logomania da Gucci e da Louis Vuitton, fivelas de ouro e estampas de medusa da Versace, prints florais caricatos da Dolce & Gabbana: essas são algumas características que dispensam explicação em relação ao poder aquisitivo de quem está usando. Basta bater o olho para entender que esse alguém pagou um valor alto pelo look.

Contudo, o quiet luxury prega justamente o contrário. Para os adeptos do luxo silencioso, o que vale é investir em bons produtos de altíssima qualidade, mas que não exalam o custo elevado.

As pessoas que seguem essa trend são muito exigentes em relação à qualidade e acabamento dos produtos que adquirem e estão dispostas a pagar mais por itens que atendam a esses critérios.

Sendo assim, a tendência quiet luxury se refere a um estilo de vida mais sofisticado e luxuoso sem ostentação. 

O objetivo da tendência quiet luxury é transmitir uma imagem de sofisticação e elegância através de uma abordagem mais discreta e consciente. 

Se você está interessado em descobrir como incorporar essa tendência em sua própria vida, ou simplesmente quer saber mais sobre as ideias por trás do "quiet luxury", não deixe de assistir a este vídeo!

Tenho certeza de que você encontrará muitas informações e insights valiosos sobre este tema. Então vem conferir algumas ideias de looks para aderir a essa trend!

items.Video_Title: HOW TO STYLE QUIET LUXURY LOOKS TO LOOK EFFORTLESS AND ALWAYS PUT TOGETHER
items.Video_Description:
HOW TO STYLE QUIET LUXURY LOOKS TO LOOK EFFORTLESS AND ALWAYS PUT TOGETHER

Styling quiet luxury looks involves combining understated elegance, high-quality materials, and impeccable tailoring. In today's video are some tips to achieve a quiet luxury looks to look effortless and chic.

Quiet luxury refers to a concept that combines high-quality craftsmanship, exclusivity, and refined elegance with a more understated and discreet approach. It represents a shift away from flashy displays of wealth and ostentatious branding towards a more subtle and sophisticated aesthetic.

Quiet luxury focuses on understated design, exceptional materials, and meticulous attention to detail. It is characterized by a sense of exclusivity and exclusivity and embraces a minimalist and timeless style. Instead of prominently displaying logos or brand names, quiet luxury emphasizes the quality and craftsmanship of the product.
Quiet luxury extends beyond physical goods and can be applied to experiences as well. It encompasses personalized and tailored services that provide a sense of exclusivity and privacy. This could include private access to exclusive events, discreet concierge services, or intimate and secluded luxury travel experiences.
The appeal of quiet luxury lies in its ability to convey a sense of sophistication and discernment without the need for overt displays of wealth. It attracts individuals who appreciate the finer things in life but value subtlety, exclusivity, and the intrinsic qualities of a product or experience rather than its outward showmanship.
